column2:
"...Alright, let's begin. I am familiar
working with you during explorations,
so there is nothing else to highlight. "

"...what is this that I am feeling?
I want to be well-honed by the photons
as soon as possible."

"...Nonetheless we still have to
proceed cautiously without being
overconfident about our techniques."

"……それじゃあ、始めましょう。
貴方との探索はもう慣れっこだし
特に確認することも、ないわよね。"

"……何かしら、この感覚？
早くもフォトンが研ぎ澄まされて
いるみたい。"

"……でもフォトンを過信せず
慎重に進んでみて。"
